Listen on Server1 0.0.0.0:4455
Send traffic to 192.168.0.2:445
Using ssh on admin@172.0.0.2
N will prevent shell

$ ssh -N -L 0.0.0.0:4455:192.168.0.2:445 admin@172.0.0.2
